ill oneself 实现抱负","headword":"fulfill oneself"},{"type":"entry","text":"fully develop 充分发展","headword":"fully develop"}]},{"number":998,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"increase productivity 提高生产率","headword":"increase productivity"},{"type":"entry","text":"job satisfaction 工作满足感","headword":"job satisfaction"},{"type":"entry","text":"skill development 技能发展","headword":"skill development"},{"type":"section","text":"Step2 学以致用"},{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 1"},{"type":"example","text":"A：We still conduct long-term training with our staff.（我们仍然对"},{"type":"text","text":"员工进行长期培训。）"},{"type":"example","text":"B：That's good. May I join in? （这真不错。我能参加吗？）"},{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 2"},{"type":"example","text":"A：I'm not qualified for the training course.（我没有资格参加培训"},{"type":"text","text":"课程。）"},{"type":"example","text":"B：Don't lose your heart; you still have a lot of chances. （别灰心，"},{"type":"text","text":"你还有很多机会。）"}]}]}